{"tid":2344473,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"見工話自己喺洗讚小鴨鴨xd;$做過，俾HR趕走咗","createTime":"2020-12-28T18:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T00:03:01.000Z","uid":97606,"like":17,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d2a7aab8c8d65fb42c0301c2de507f230a3fe2bd","tid":2344473,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T18:11:56.000Z","msg":"考衰咗dse之後一直留喺屋企做廢人，<br />\n去到近排武肺老豆俾人炒咗，話如果我再唔出去搵工就趕我出街，<br />\n臨急臨忙就求其打咗份CV，第一次搵工乜都唔識，入面啲個人資料乜柒乜柒9成9都係Facebook照copy and paste，<br />\n結果今朝見工俾人問工作經驗個到寫Facebook係乜意思，<br />\n原本諗住唔想人知冇返過工所以求其寫啲嘢落去，點知會俾人問，<br />\n我咪答佢：係FB上面果啲本地企業囉......<br />\n跟住佢追問：咁姐係咩類型嘅公司，有冇名？<br />\n我就口窒窒咁話：係間大......大公司嚟......請好多人嘅......個名叫......叫洗讚小鴨鴨xd;$......<br />\n之後個HR就黑哂面咁叫我返去等消息了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下係咪誠實答話自己冇做過嘢會仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5df74ec16dbe20b953ef3e85b9e4c2b8e7acfb","tid":2344473,"uid":249378,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T18:22:25.000Z","msg":"咩黎真心1999"},{"pid":"33c7643b5d50a5b952c10edd475c3048cedbde94","tid":2344473,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eb5df74ec16dbe20b953ef3e85b9e4c2b8e7acfb","tid":2344473,"uid":249378,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T18:22:25.000Z","msg":"咩黎真心1999"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T18:25:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce52020799903760cdbb564338448533fa76adb","tid":2344473,"uid":195223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T18:36:43.000Z","msg":"話讀齊齊哈爾同鄉會林天光紀念中學就會有人請xdd"},{"pid":"b75f0d3cc248967fb3cb19a86dd78ac57f357ab4","tid":2344473,"uid":97606,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T18:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hxNcAAT.png\" d